title: Die veneris 25. die Novemb. 1664. The Lords spiritual and temporal in the High Court of Parliament assembled, do hereby require every member of this house not to grant any protection or protections (during this present session of Parliament) to any person or persons that are not, or shall not be their lordships menial servants  ...
